<p>After Punjab Police withdrew the Z+ security, the Centre stepped in and granted him Z category security cover. According to reports, Delhi Police has already been instructed to provide him with immediate protection until a full central security arrangement is put in place.</p>

<p>The change in security arrangements has also led to speculation about Chadha’s political future. In recent days, he has shared several social media posts that many people believe were indirect messages to the AAP leadership. One of his posts included the phrase “Never Outshine the Master,” which many interpreted as a reference to internal party politics.</p>

<p>There is also speculation that Chadha may be considering a different political path in the future. However, no official announcement has been made. For now, the withdrawal of his Punjab Police security and the Centre’s decision to provide him with fresh protection have added more drama to an already tense political situation.</p>

